{
  "stem": "10588.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And also, they gave us the impression-- who is old, who is sick, who is pregnant, it's hard to work-- they're going to get all right.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I said, look, it doesn't even sound like the same Nazis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was grateful at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then, the worst part was when I found out-- since we didn't know-- I never said goodbye to any of them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one thing, everything that I loved and held sacred, everything was gone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My family-- that was the last day on earth for my family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Thousands of Jews from, from the ghetto of Nowe Miasto came together in the beginning of a living hell for me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we didn't know it yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They marched us in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And from the start, I lost freedom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were taken to a place where there's supposed to be-- told us we were going to take a bath.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was clutching a little photograph in my-- everything was thrown away but a little photograph from my family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The told me to give it to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I didn't want to, so I got beaten.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I realized later that I might get killed, so I gave away the last shred of my past.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They put on a tattoo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Mine was two, five, six, seven, three, which means that 25,673 people before me had those numbers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "However, those that they sent to the gas chamber, they didn't put on numbers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So what seemed a misfortune at that time-- found out I have a number.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The others didn't have numbers, but neither do they have life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And later, they shaved our hair, heads, and all hair in any private places.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
